sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant ScreenReader as Screen Reader
    participant Application as Application
    participant Keyboard as Keyboard Navigation
    participant Support as Support Team

    User->>ScreenReader: Activate screen reader
    ScreenReader->>Application: Request content
    Application->>ScreenReader: Provide accessible content
    User->>Keyboard: Navigate using keyboard
    Keyboard->>Application: Send navigation commands
    Application->>Keyboard: Respond with focus updates
    User->>Support: Report issues with navigation
    Support->>Application: Investigate reported issues
    Application->>Support: Provide feedback on fixes
    Support->>User: Communicate resolution